name: James Lamb
text: Shopping in the Outlet mall I don't want to leave and come back.  The food court is one worth eating at and my favorite is the South Philly.  Quick and good quality ingredients.  Very diverse selection of choices to make everyone happy.  Best part, no lost travel time. You can do what you want, Shop.
